T02TD2137E:196b-1: ku la lo ki shva ra s'a dha nam /
T02TD2137E:196b-3: rigs kyi 'jig rten dbang phyug sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD2137E:196b-4: de nas bdag gis bshad par bya //
T02TD2137E:196b-5: rigs 'jig dbang phyug sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD2137E:196b-6: gsang sngags rigs kyi rim pa ni //
T02TD2137E:196b-7: bla ma'i zhal las rjes su thob //
T02TD2137E:196b-8: mtshan mo tha ma'i brgyad cha lus //
T02TD2137E:196b-9: thugs rje'i bdag nyid langs nas ni //
T02TD2137E:196b-11: skyil krung bcas la 'dug par bya //
T02TD2137E:196b-12: bdud rtsi lnga ni blangs nas su //
T02TD2137E:196b-13: thod par rtog med sems kyis gzhag / shes rab can gyis me rlung ste //
T02TD2137E:196b-14: dag dang khol dang 'bar bar bya //
T02TD2137E:196b-15: rnal 'byor skyes phyir phyi dang ni //
T02TD2137E:196b-16: nang gi gzugs ni dag par bya //
T02TD2137E:196b-17: de rjes thugs kar padma dang //
T02TD2137E:196b-18: nyi ma'i dbus su hr'i:bsgom bya //
T02TD2137E:196b-19: khams gsum ma lus khyab pa yi //
T02TD2137E:196b-21: bla mas sangs rgyas 'jig rten mgon //
T02TD2137E:196b-22: spyan drangs nas ni mchod par bya //
T02TD2137E:196b-23: de rjes rang bzhin stong pa nyid ;
T02TD2137E:196b-24: / sems ni cung zad nam mkha'o //
T02TD2137E:196b-25: de las langs nas phyogs bcur yang //
T02TD2137E:196b-26: khro bo bcu ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD2137E:196b-27: dpag tshad bye snyed tshad du ni //
T02TD2137E:196b-28: rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor bsgom par bya //
T02TD2137E:196b-29: de yi dkyil du rang gi lus //
T02TD2137E:196b-30: khru bzhi po ni mnyam pa po //
T02TD2137E:196b-31: ka ba brgyad ldan sgo bzhi pa //
T02TD2137E:196b-32: thar pa yi ni grong mchog ltos ;
T02TD2137E:196b-33: / de dbus chos kyi padma la //
T02TD2137E:196b-34: 'char kha nyi ma'i steng du ni //
T02TD2137E:196b-35: shes rab thabs kyi yi ge las //
T02TD2137E:196b-36: mchog gi padma mdzes pa skyes //
T02TD2137E:196b-38: rnam pa lnga ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD2137E:196b-39: de gyur pa las bdag nyid ni //
T02TD2137E:196b-40: rigs 'jig dbang phyug khyab bdag ni //
T02TD2137E:197a-2: zhal gcig ral pa 'chang ba po //
T02TD2137E:197a-3: cung zad mche gtsigs mi bzang pa //
T02TD2137E:197a-4: padma gar dbang dpral bar brgyan //
T02TD2137E:197a-5: zla ba nyi ma me yi spyan //
T02TD2137E:197a-6: de yi dkyil du rang gi lus //
T02TD2137E:197a-7: khru bzhi bo ni mnyam pa po //
T02TD2137E:197a-8: phyag bzhi par ni blta bar bya //
T02TD2137E:197a-9: rdo rje skyil krung gis gnas pa //
T02TD2137E:197a-10: sgeg ba'i nyams kyis yongs gang ba //
T02TD2137E:197a-11: g-yas pa mchog sbyin lcags kyu dang //
T02TD2137E:197a-13: dpa' bo phyag rgya drug gis brgyan //
T02TD2137E:197a-14: padma'i phreng ba'i do shal can //
T02TD2137E:197a-15: de yi thugs kar bsgom bya ba //
T02TD2137E:197a-16: hr'im gi yi ge dmar po las //
T02TD2137E:197a-18: ye shes 'khor lo gzhug par bya //
T02TD2137E:197a-19: de nas bde gshegs dngos grub kun //
T02TD2137E:197a-20: ster la dbang bskur mdzad par gsol //
T02TD2137E:197a-21: rlung gi sngags kyi phreng ba'o //
T02TD2137E:197a-23: ha cang myur bul ma yin pas //
T02TD2137E:197a-24: yi ge yi ge 'brel bar bya //
T02TD2137E:197a-25: sngags kyi bzlas pa 'bum phrag gcig / sum cu rtsa gsum pa blang bya //
T02TD2137E:197a-26: ra ni 'og tu gdan du bya //
T02TD2137E:197a-27: bzhi pa sbyar bar brtan pa la //
T02TD2137E:197a-29: aushma na yi bzhi pa zung //
T02TD2137E:197a-30: drug pa gdan du ldan pa'o //
T02TD2137E:197a-31: stong ba dbu la lce gnyis pa //
T02TD2137E:197a-32: tsheg drag gnyis ni blta bar bya //
T02TD2137E:197a-33: 'di ltar yi ge don mang po //
T02TD2137E:197a-34: gnyis med ye shes kyis rtogs 'gyur //
T02TD2137E:197a-35: bla ma'i man ngag lam gyis ni //
T02TD2137E:197a-36: rim pa rgyas par rtogs par bya //
T02TD2137E:197a-37: rna nas rna ru brgyud pa yis //
T02TD2137E:197a-38: gsang ba mchog gis zhi ba yi //
T02TD2137E:197a-39: brjod pas myur du grub pa thob //
T02TD2137E:197a-40: bdud sngags zlog par byed mi nus //
T02TD2137E:197a-41: dang por bsnyen pa'i cho ga bya //
T02TD2137E:197a-42: mnyam par gzhag pas khri bzlas bya//
T02TD2137E:197a-43: mi gang bsod nams dman pa la //
T02TD2137E:197a-45: zhags pa lcags kyu stag sham thabs //
T02TD2137E:197a-46: rtse gcig sems kyis sgom byed na //
T02TD2137E:197a-48: brtan dang g-yo ba dbang du 'gyur //
T02TD2137E:197a-49: rang gi snying gar bu brgyad langs //
T02TD2137E:197a-50: sna bug g-yas las phyir phyung ste //
T02TD2137E:197a-51: bsgrub bya'i sna bug g-yon par gzhug / snying ga'i blo ni dgug par bya //
T02TD2137E:197a-52: de ltar yang yang cho ga ni //
T02TD2137E:197a-53: dbang du ma gyur bar du bya //
T02TD2137E:197a-54: bsgrub bya rkang pa'i 'og tu bsam //
T02TD2137E:197a-55: khol po lta bur 'gyur ba yin //
T02TD2137E:197a-56: khyab 'jug me lha dbang phyug che //
T02TD2137E:197a-57: dbang po klu dang srin po srog / sngags kyi rgyal po'i nus pa yis//
T02TD2137E:197b-0: @197b skad cig nyid la dbang du 'gyur //
T02TD2137E:197b-1: de nas phyi rol mchog cho ga / mnyam par gzhag pa'i rnal 'byor bya //
T02TD2137E:197b-2: zha nye las byung ches dmar ba //
T02TD2137E:197b-3: gru drug 'khor lo bri bar bya //
T02TD2137E:197b-4: de yi nang du dpa' bo bri //
T02TD2137E:197b-6: dang por smos pa'i cho ga ni //
T02TD2137E:197b-7: ts'a ru sna tshogs lha bshos dang //
T02TD2137E:197b-8: ba la sna tshogs ma da na //
T02TD2137E:197b-9: mang pos gzhon nu ma yang mchod //
T02TD2137E:197b-10: de bzhin mkha' 'gro ma kun yang //
T02TD2137E:197b-11: sna tshogs rnga chen pa ta ha //
T02TD2137E:197b-12: glu dang rol mo yid 'phrog ma //
T02TD2137E:197b-13: me tog sna tshogs cho ga yang //
T02TD2137E:197b-14: rdo rje 'dzin gyis mnyes par bya //
T02TD2137E:197b-15: de nas gtor ma'i las bya ste //
T02TD2137E:197b-16: rnal 'byor dbang phyug nub tu blta //
T02TD2137E:197b-17: sba grol gcer bu byas nas ni //
T02TD2137E:197b-18: langs te rkang pa g-yon pa brkyang //
T02TD2137E:197b-19: de nas padma'i phyag rgyas sbyin //
T02TD2137E:197b-22: thams cad dngos grub 'bras bu nye //
T02TD2137E:197b-23: aom a'a: a'a ro li ka yi mam panytsa aa mri ta ba lim bra t'i tstsha grihna ma ma sarbba kar yam sa ha ya h'um phat /
T02TD2137E:197b-24: de lta bu ni au rgyan dpal //
T02TD2137E:197b-26: bla ma mkha' 'gro ma'i zhal las //
T02TD2137E:197b-27: thob nas bdag la bshad pa mdzad //
T02TD2137E:197b-28: rigs kyi 'jig rten dbang phyug sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02TD2137E:197b-29: slob dpon bhri dhi ra bram zes mdzad pa 'jam dpal sgeg pas bsgyur ba rdzogs so//
